  <tr>
    <td align="left" valign="top"><font face="Verdana" size="2">
    very wierd.  A quiver will hold 20 arrows in 4 slots of 20 each.  Full quiver/ empty quiver seem to wiegh the exact same.  If you have an arrow in your ammo slot, quiver will automatically put another there when you fire bow. I am told home-made quiver has 6 slots.  DON'T BUY THIS ITEM!!!  All of these abilities (except hand made 6 slot) are duplicated by the PURSE!  It has been driving me crazy all week.  Purse costs 2 silver pieces, Quiver costs 2 platinum.  The only difference I have been able to discover is that i can put small items and stackable items in purse, and I can only put arrows in quiver, yet quiver costs 100 times purse. (That's approx 200 arrows for those of us that don't make arrows)
		</font>
    </td>
  </tr>
  
